    "Id": "vehicledef_Katydid",
    "Name": "Katydid WCV",
    "Details": "Created as a support vehicle for battlemech lances, the Katydid Wheeled Combat Vehicle is an 80 ton fire support vehicle. Powered by a 300 rated fusion engine, the Katydid is capable of reaching a speed of 60kph while carrying 11 tons of ferro-fibrous armor. Mounted in the turret is an Artemis IV enhanced LRM-15 and a RAC/5, with a pair of Medium Pulse Lasers providing backup at closer ranges.\n\n<b><color=#ffcc00>Biome Restrictions: None.</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#ffcc00>Movement: 3/5 hexes / 90/150 meters.</color></b>\n\n<color=#ffcc00><b>Armor:</b> Armor\n<b>Structure:</b> Structure\n<b>Values       A        S  </b>\n<b>Front</b>       390     40\n<b>Left</b>         275     40\n<b>Right</b>       275     40\n<b>Rear</b>        200     40\n<b>Turret</b>      350     40\n\n<b>Total</b>      1490    200</color>\n\n<color=#ff0000>Quirk: Improved Targeting - Long</color>",
    "Icon": "uixTxrIcon_katydidwheeledcv"
  },
